room_title: Escape room "The Cemetery" by The Code Escape in Tampa
room_address: 415 S. Pinellas Ave. Tarpon Springs, FL 34689
room_description: The time is deep in the Zombie Apocalypse. You are among the 27% of the population that has avoided the Virus. Use the clues to find the chemicals and activate the bomb that will save the world, killing the virus in the zombies and immunizing those not yet affected.
